The Football League Show 06.12.2014 

Duration: 40 min

Our feature match this week comes from the DW Stadium as Wigan entertain Norwich.
Fulham meanwhile welcome Watford to Craven Cottage, and we've the best of the action from the City Ground as Nottingham Forest meet Charlton.
Drama from all three divisions of the Football League brought to you by Manish Bhasin.
